<plot>With stunning visuals of sprint car racing at night, as well as aerial flight over Ohio's countryside, Chin Music captures an aging man's insight on the purpose of life. Hear the wisdom of Hans Dam as he narrates this documentary short. Chin Music was shot on film by Cincinnati-based filmmaker, Mark A. Hood.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?103506</url></doc>
